  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your oven to 180°C (350°F).",
    "Mix kielbasa, dumplings, raw honey, coconut flakes, chopped walnuts, and maple syrup in a bowl until combined.",
    "Divide the mixture into individual portions on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Sprinkle sesame seeds over each portion for extra crunch.",
    "Bake for 15-20 minutes or until golden brown.",
    "Remove from oven and let cool slightly before serving."
